    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300060640_5_1218-1312",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1218-1312",
      "markText": "今文经学派认为经书是圣人之言，字字句句寓有“微言大义”，大可经世致用，常常断章取义，任意引申比附。古文经学派认为应该根据字义客观地解释经义，应该重视语言文字之学，树立它在经学上的崇高地位。",
      "totalCount": 170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300060640&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1218&rangeEnd=1312",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8e32c20813ab7e30g010257?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1218&rangeEnd=1312"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300060640_5_1762-1808",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1762-1808",
      "markText": "许慎把庞杂的汉字分为依类象形的“文”和形声相益的“字”，倾注毕生的精力，撰写了《说文解字》。",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300060640&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1762&rangeEnd=1808",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8e32c20813ab7e30g010257?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1762&rangeEnd=1808"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300060640_5_1687-1737",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1687-1737",
      "markText": "“其于所不知，盖阙如也。”（见《说文解字叙》）对于自己不知道的东西，让它缺着，不自以为是，强作解人。",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300060640&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1687&rangeEnd=1737",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8e32c20813ab7e30g010257?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1687&rangeEnd=1737"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300060640_5_7947-8155",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "7947-8155",
      "markText": "王() 天下所归往也。董仲舒曰：“古之造文者，三画而连其中谓之王。三者，天、地、人也，而参通之者王也。”孔子曰：“一贯三为王。”",
      "totalCount": 110,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300060640&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7947&rangeEnd=8155",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8e32c20813ab7e30g010257?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7947&rangeEnd=8155"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300060640_5_746-784",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "746-784",
      "markText": "《说文解字》的产生，不是偶然的，是东汉的客观条件与许慎的主观条件碰撞的结果。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300060640&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=746&rangeEnd=784",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8e32c20813ab7e30g010257?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=746&rangeEnd=784"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300060640_5_2388-2429",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2388-2429",
      "markText": "“前人所以垂后，后人所以识古。”说明文字是超时空、超阶级的工具，是人类文明的载体。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300060640&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2388&rangeEnd=2429",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8e32c20813ab7e30g010257?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2388&rangeEnd=2429"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300060640_5_1150-1167",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1150-1167",
      "markText": "今文是指隶书，古文是指先秦六国古文",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300060640&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1150&rangeEnd=1167",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8e32c20813ab7e30g010257?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1150&rangeEnd=1167"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300060640_5_2429-2467",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2429-2467",
      "markText": "文字虽然没有阶级性，但在有阶级的社会里，却是统治者维护统治的最重要工具之一。",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300060640&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2429&rangeEnd=2467",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8e32c20813ab7e30g010257?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2429&rangeEnd=2467"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300060640_5_5089-5165",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "5089-5165",
      "markText": "但是不管人们怎么改并，不管有多大进展，在漫长的1900年间，许氏的部首制，作为一种检字的系统，谁也没有从根本上改变它，甚至可以断言，它将始终与汉字同在。",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300060640&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5089&rangeEnd=5165",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8e32c20813ab7e30g010257?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5089&rangeEnd=5165"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300060640_5_10311-10408",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "10311-10408",
      "markText": "《说文解字》也十分重视“义傅于音”的现象。音和义本来没有必然的联系，由于联想的作用，人们往往用相同或相似的声音来表示相同或相似的意义，这就出现音、义相依的现象，这种现象必然反映到汉字的构形中来。",
      "totalCount": 84,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300060640&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=10311&rangeEnd=10408",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8e32c20813ab7e30g010257?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=10311&rangeEnd=10408"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300060640_7_2780-2808",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2780-2808",
      "markText": "造此类字与今日大写的壹贰叁等十字同一目的，是为了防诈伪。",
      "totalCount": 84,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300060640&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2780&rangeEnd=2808",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8e32c20813ab7e30g010257?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2780&rangeEnd=2808"
    },
    {
