      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "9378-9437",
      "markText": "象形者，实有其物，日、月是也。指事者，不泥其物而言其事，丄、丅是也。天地为形，天在上，地在下；地在上，天在下：则皆为事",
      "totalCount": 84,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300060640&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=9378&rangeEnd=9437",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8e32c20813ab7e30g010257?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=9378&rangeEnd=9437"
    },
    {
